name: FIFTYONEFIFTY
description: The 5150 token will act as web3 authentication to our members area, where the token will be used to interact with our NFT ecosystem. This quarantined area will provide exclusive auctions to members on rare items, provide a tradable marketplace for our NFTs series of prints and collectibles, and act as currency for our future gameplay. Additionally, wallets that hold 5150 token will be airdropped random items from our unpublished “Collectibles” series.
